definition: to have/there is/there are/to exist/to be
to wait/to treat/to deal with/to need/going to (do sth)/about to/intending to

sentences.english: Chinese culture sees all non-Chinese as sub-human, to be exploited.
sentences.chinese: 中國文化把所有的其他人種視爲有待剝削的次等民族。

sentences.english: Whether TTV is a hepatitis viral remains further study.
sentences.chinese: TTV是否嗜肝病毒，有待進一步研究。

sentences.english: Conclusion The medication for treating the patients with IGAN in our hospital is essentially reasonable except for a few cases.
sentences.chinese: 該類疾病治療藥物的合理應用仍有待進一步研究。

sentences.english: Some crucial questions about the subject still remain to beanswered.
sentences.chinese: 和課題有關的一些關鍵問題仍然有待於研究。

sentences.english: But even the new satellite-based radar images still need fine-tuning.
sentences.chinese: 不過即使是新型衛星雷達圖像仍有待調整。

sentences.english: But the safety of precut EPT remains controversial.
sentences.chinese: 但內視鏡乳突先前切開術之安全性有待評估。

sentences.english: For CPE to be used as an anti_tumor agent awaits further studies.
sentences.chinese: 香加皮作爲抗腫瘤藥物有待進一步開發研究。

sentences.english: But this leaves some big questions to be answered.
sentences.chinese: 但是，這留下了一些大問題有待解決。

sentences.english: But we have further to go with this simile.
sentences.chinese: 但是關於這個比喻我們還有更多有待發現的。

sentences.english: The present representatives' quality is yet to be improved.
sentences.chinese: 目前的人大代表素質尚有待於提高。

sentences.english: The wisest mind has something yet to learn.
sentences.chinese: 上智的心靈乃仍然有待學之處。

sentences.english: Further research on how to control the content of heavy metal in Bombyx Batryticatus should be well developed.
sentences.chinese: 如何控制殭蠶中的重金屬含量有待深入研究。

sentences.english: A new-type stethoscope has yet to be invented.
sentences.chinese: 新型的聽診器有待發明。

sentences.english: Finally, some basic optical waveguide theory problems, which are waiting for consideration in optical waveguide technique developement, are proposal.
sentences.chinese: 提出了光波導技術發展中有待於考慮的若干基本問題。

sentences.english: It's debatable whether it was good for everybody.
sentences.chinese: 是否有利於所有人，有待商榷。

sentences.english: This kind of equity-based compensation system still involves widely disputes and needs further improvement.
sentences.chinese: 這種權益爲主的報酬體制仍存在廣泛爭議，有待完善。
